HEADWORD: Ill-starred
<hw>Ill"-starred`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Fated to be
unfortunate; unlucky; <as>as, an <ex>ill-starred</ex> man or
day</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ill-fated, ill-omened, unlucky.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

